<A>__{from rafe and danny's pov, the rush is awesome. the pilots on the ground watch in awe as the p 40's get so close they can't possibly get out of each other's way. billy, the most boyish faced of the pilots, yells to drown out the sound of the collision... at the last instant, both planes snap a quarter turn so that their wings are vertical, and they shoot past each other belly to belly.}
