<A>__{the p 40, hurtling toward the ground at nauseating speed, snaps into a half roll, streaking upside down over the runway. rafe hangs inverted in his flight harness, the asphalt of the runway shooting past, ten feet beyond his head. he pushes the plane into a climb, his cockpit on the outside of the circle. the plane reaches the top of its arc, and almost stalls; but rafe noses it over again, toward the earth, only this time he has very little altitude. the plane hurtles down, still with it belly on the inside of the curve... and makes it full circle. rafe's head now is barely a foot off the asphalt as the plane shoots past, still inverted. the other pilots burst into cheers. rafe, in his cockpit permits himself a smile. he lands, and the guys run out to meet him...all except for the training captain, who stands there shaking his head. danny jumps on the wing, as rafe stops and slides back his canopy. danny grabs him by the harness and shakes him.}
